text: @FedEx @FedExHelp I had scheduled a pick up for today and the executive promised me that they will pick up my box from my home today. Now I have got a call from your Aluva, Kerala branch saying that they can't pick my item. What is this? Your service is really worst in Kerala.

@SibeeshVenu Hello, this is Christopher. My apologies, the U.S. FedEx Social Media team can assist with U.S to U.S domestic concerns only. Please contact India

1 800-22-6161

india@fedex.com

We appreciate your business and the opportunity to assist you.

-Christopher
@FedExIndia @FedEx @FedExHelp I have shared the information. Please check your inbox. Thanks
